-They are going back to Moscow by foot 
-Young guys...
-Are you leaving us? (Sarcastic but rather nice form to address)
-Yes as promissed
-Good, glory to Ukraine.
-Did you pick all your goods? (Women asking)
-Return home (man asking nicely)
-Guys have you planted some mines there? Guys ? 
-No
-Any booby traps ? There are kids playing there
-No, it's all good.
-Return home safe, try not to get killed. 

Edit
Respect to these guys. Russians Soldiers like these that refuse to follow illegitimate orders are as heroic as the Ukrainians that fight back, as both put their lives on the line trying to resist tyranny

Some russian POW reported that they never knew they were invading Ukraine, that they thought it was still a part of military exercise.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sXMNRhA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[uebermacht]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>met this couple on my walk and it made my day</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RF8gOQM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RyllK41.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(Posted with permission)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RF8gOQM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zoraniko]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Funny</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YURd1gl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jzeNhlk.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YURd1gl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Current events dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/f9SHFYv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SY59C68.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>All memes shamelessly stolen and 0% fact checked. Enjoy my friends!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UNUDAhg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IMnkCIY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LXQKFnE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h4R5ipb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xT85V6A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b0hHjZ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%;